docs.lead_paragraph: ETHEREUM CHALLENGES BITCOIN | A new virtual gold rush is under way. Ethereum, a rival to Bitcoin, has soared in value and climbed 1,000 percent over the last three months,Nathaniel Popper reports in DealBook. Ethereum’s rise has attracted attention from giants like JPMorgan Chase, Microsoft and IBM.

docs.abstract: Amazon, Google, IBM and Microsoft are using high salaries and games pitting humans against computers to try to claim the standard on which all companies will build their A.I. technology.

docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — The resounding win by a Google artificial intelligence program over a champion in the complex board game Go this month was a statement — not so much to professional game players as to Google’s competitors.
